title: This Tech Giant Kicks Off Q1 Earnings Season Tomorrow, But Shares Are Falling Ahead Of The Release
text: September 15, 2015 at 21:00 PM EDT This Tech Giant Kicks Off Q1 Earnings Season Tomorrow, But Shares Are Falling Ahead Of The Release Software Giant Oracle will be releasing its Fiscal Q1 2016 earnings Wednesday after market close. Wall street analysts are expecting an EPS of $0.52 and revenue of $8.511 billion.
